{"tid":713913,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［PC]［Discord]香港的綜合遊戲台","createTime":"2018-06-23T08:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T22:07:11.000Z","uid":104239,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb163fb998a70c7fda947146a58f0b868f7b60bf","tid":713913,"uid":104239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:29:25.000Z","msg":"經過過往的遊戲台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n缺乏管理員的管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大量的小學雞係遊戲文字頻道洗頻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以及不停進出語音頻道影響玩家體驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我決定<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望開一個高質的遊戲台</span></span>聚集全港玩家共同創造一個舒適以及高質的遊戲台@若有類似事件發生管理員會盡快第一時間處理<br />\n如有需要可向管理員申請<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 專屬頻道</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">申請條件必須要活躍高以及5位玩家以上</span><br />\n不久將來會陸續增加不同遊戲的頻道<br />\n如：@GTA@RAINBOW6@LOL@&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;如此類推<br />\n希望各位玩家多多支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/c9FhaAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2Fc9FhaAw&d=%2BbDes5M%2BhYKS2GX4MBi%2Bk54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4201019d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/c9FhaAw</a>"},{"pid":"e63d9528d122a91e72638eb4606fedaadc0689bb","tid":713913,"uid":104239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:08:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cae774d7134ca9ceb3fa588335196290b1d39b","tid":713913,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:07:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}